{
  "name": "WorldOS 本地 RC 验收产物策略 v1",
  "updatedAt": "2026-07-06",
  "summary": "release:local-rc 是唯一推荐的本地可信 RC 入口；提交时只提交有复核价值的规范化证据，临时日志留在 reports/。",
  "recommendedCommand": "npm run release:local-rc",
  "compatibleCommand": "npm run check:rc:full",
  "canonicalCommittedEvidence": [
    "docs/90-archive/reports/worldos-local-rc-summary-report.json",
    "docs/90-archive/reports/worldos-local-runtime-smoke-report.json",
    "docs/90-archive/reports/worldos-local-lan-rc-report.json",
    "docs/90-archive/reports/npm-audit-report.json",
    "docs/90-archive/reports/worldos-external-evidence-template.json",
    "docs/90-archive/reports/worldos-local-lan-rc/*.png",
    "public/world-index.json",
    "public/world-manifest.json"
  ],
  "ephemeralEvidence": [
    "reports/worldos-local-lan-rc-next-start.log",
    "reports/worldos-local-lan-rc-chrome.log",
    "reports/worldos-local-runtime-smoke-next-start.log",
    "reports/*.tmp",
    ".next/**"
  ],
  "diffPolicy": [
    "summary、runtime、LAN、audit 和截图证据只应在执行 release:local-rc 后提交。",
    "仅 generatedAt 或运行时日志变化不足以构成有价值提交；提交前优先检查是否存在源码、配置、截图或门禁结论变化。",
    "截图用于证明 desktop、mobile-reduced-motion 和关键首屏区域；视觉变化应和对应代码或样式变化一起提交。",
    "reports/ 下的进程日志是排障材料，不作为规范提交产物。"
  ],
  "requiredSummaryLinks": [
